channel.title: Singapore does not exist on the Map
channel.description:
Singapore does not exist on redash's map visualization.
Singapore is a small island nation located south of Malaysia, but I believe it is pretty well known in the world by its futuristic looking buildings and sea lion statute. Westworld season 4 was filmed in Singapore and many cool futuristic buildings were shown in the show!
![image|690x441](upload://oss5UCVnLkLyTpBDsFZeOnzAilX.png)
Please add Singapore to the map visualization.
